# version 2 (see:
# http://docs.mathjax.org/en/v2.7-latest/output.html) and MathJax version 3
# (see:
# http://docs.mathjax.org/en/latest/web/components/output.html).
# Possible values are: HTML-CSS (which is slower, but has the best
